name: International Aeronautical & Aerospace Conference
content: Outlook Conferences is pleased to welcome you all for "International Aeronautical and Aerospace Conference (OLCAAC-2019)", which will be held, at Venice, Italy during November 14-15, 2019, aims to become the leading annual conference in fields related to Aeroelasticity and structural dynamics. This conference have an elemental feature to the world with a great knowledge and new ideas to their research work with the community and speakers, plenary speeches, young Investigators & Researchers Forum, poster presentations, oral presentations, technical workshop and scientific sessions.
